solution: ```class Solution {
    public int minInsertions(String s) {
        int openNeeded = 0;
        int closeNeeded = 0;
        for (char c : s.toCharArray()) {
            if (c == '(') {
                if (closeNeeded % 2 != 0) {
                    closeNeeded++;
                    openNeeded++;
                }
                closeNeeded += 2;
            } else {
                closeNeeded--;
                if (closeNeeded < 0) {
                    openNeeded++;
                    closeNeeded += 2;
                }
            }
        }
        return openNeeded + closeNeeded;
    }
}
```
efficiency: HIGH
time complexity: O(n)
space complexity: O(1)
energy implications: LOW
explanation: Single pass counts unmatched opens and closes; odd close deficit is fixed by one extra close and one open; negative close deficit triggers an open insertion and resets close deficit to 1.

